<p>We‚Äôll be building our site from the ground up with <em>no Blazor experience required</em>. All you‚Äôll need is a passing knowledge of C# and .NET. If you don‚Äôt have that, no problem: brush up on some C# (I enjoy <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/learn/paths/csharp-first-steps/">this Learn module</a>) and come back when you‚Äôre ready.</p>

